Title: Merry Monster Survey
Description: Watch videos and answer questions to learn new words (45-75 minutes)!
Answer.Comments:
I thought this study was likely testing how closing participants paid attention to the video and how quickly they were to click on items, especially the questions about the +.  Several times the study would automatically advance to the next question after very briefly displaying the question about the +.  In fact, several times the question barely loaded at all before it was gone.  I wanted to mention that in case it was unintended.

I noticed that the more I thought about what the initial action was in the first video describing the verb, the less likely I was to notice the + symbol at the end of the video, regardless of how much time it was displayed.
